        Created by Canonical Ltd. <http://www.canonical.com/> and licensed
        under the Ubuntu Font License Version 1.0
        <http://font.ubuntu.com/licence/>, available at
        <http://font.ubuntu.com/>.

    *   backgound.png

        Based on spacefield_a-000.png created by beren77
        <http://opengameart.org/user/453> and licensed under the Public
        Domain, available at
        <http://opengameart.org/content/space-backdrop>.

    *   explosion.png

        Based on an image from jswars_gfx_cc3.zip created by Jonas Wagner
        <http://29a.ch/> and licensed under CC-BY-SA 3.0
        <http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/legalcode>, available
        at
        <http://opengameart.org/content/asteroid-explosions-rocket-mine-and-
        laser>.

