        Based on ship360_32.png created by Killy Overdrive
        <http://www.killyoverdrive.co.cc/> and licensed under CC-BY 3.0
        <http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/legalcode>, available at
        <http://opengameart.org/content/spaceship-360>.

